      "writtenOn": "2026-05-26T14:28:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Those fields are set by `init_iterator_data()` and `fill_iterator_data()`.\n`data.ost` is set if the file is not a directory and `data.has_extension` is set to true if the lustre layout has the LCME_FL_EXTENSION flag.\nThose are used in the following fuction `xattrs_fill_layout`, to decide whether to fill some pairs or not, but no check was done to ensure the created pairs could fit in the available space.",
